   1 # -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
   2 
   3 """
   4     Extension for the python ``click`` module to provide
   5     a group with a git-like *did-you-mean* feature.
   6 """
   7 
   8 import click
   9 import difflib
  10 
  11 __version__ = "0.0.3"
  12 
  13 
  14 class DYMMixin(object):  # pylint: disable=too-few-public-methods
  15     """
  16     Mixin class for click MultiCommand inherited classes
  17     to provide git-like *did-you-mean* functionality when
  18     a certain command is not registered.
  19     """
  20     def __init__(self, *args, **kwargs):
  21         self.max_suggestions = kwargs.pop("max_suggestions", 3)
  22         self.cutoff = kwargs.pop("cutoff", 0.5)
  23         super(DYMMixin, self).__init__(*args, **kwargs)
  24 
  25     def resolve_command(self, ctx, args):
  26         """
  27         Overrides clicks ``resolve_command`` method
  28         and appends *Did you mean ...* suggestions
  29         to the raised exception message.
  30         """
  31         original_cmd_name = click.utils.make_str(args[0])
  32 
  33         try:
  34             return super(DYMMixin, self).resolve_command(ctx, args)
  35         except click.exceptions.UsageError as error:
  36             error_msg = str(error)
  37             matches = difflib.get_close_matches(original_cmd_name,
  38                                                 self.list_commands(ctx), self.max_suggestions, self.cutoff)
  39             if matches:
  40                 error_msg += '\n\nDid you mean one of these?\n    %s' % '\n    '.join(matches)  # pylint: disable=line-too-long
  41 
  42             raise click.exceptions.UsageError(error_msg, error.ctx)
  43 
  44 
  45 class DYMGroup(DYMMixin, click.Group):  # pylint: disable=too-many-public-methods
  46     """
  47     click Group to provide git-like
  48     *did-you-mean* functionality when a certain
  49     command is not found in the group.
  50     """
  51 
  52 
  53 class DYMCommandCollection(DYMMixin, click.CommandCollection):  # pylint: disable=too-many-public-methods
  54     """
  55     click CommandCollection to provide git-like
  56     *did-you-mean* functionality when a certain
  57     command is not found in the group.
  58     """
